      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "从我七岁的时候，我是个孤儿，若不是老爷子救了我，我早就淹死在海里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "所以你对宫家的人，一直都很忠心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "曼姑娘如果想跟我聊天，到了小艇上我们一定有很多时间可以聊。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "九少爷是个怎么样的人，你当然很清楚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "现在陆小凤去找他了，这一去很可能不会回来。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "他一死，宫主也得死，我们就没有一个人能活，所以……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "所以我有句话一定要先跟你说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "这句话曼姑娘是不是一定要现在说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这句话只有三个字。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "三个字？哪三个字？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
