      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "现在我们是在冒险，可是如果没有你，我们就连这种机会都得不到，所以，如果我们这次都能活下去，我希望你能永远跟我们在一起。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我是个很会吃醋的女人，可是这次我说的是真心话。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "我今年已经十六岁了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "陆小凤是个很讨人喜欢的男人，我相信一定有很多女孩子都喜欢他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
