      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你喜欢什么？喜欢沙曼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你若以为那女人是个淑女，你就错了，她是婊子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她是个不折不扣的婊子，为了块肥肉就肯陪人上床睡觉，她十三岁的时候就已经陪人上床睡觉。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
