      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你是不是已明白了？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "明白什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你刚才并没有错，因为你根本没有机会。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "所以，你也不必对我感激。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以你现在非死不可了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "无论谁做出了不该做的事，都非死不可。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "何况我还看见了一些不该看的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只可惜现在我还不能杀你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "因为你从不免费杀人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为了你，这一点我也可破例。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
