      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你怕死，可是你来了，你当然不是来送死的。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你准备用她的命，来换你们两条命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "不是两条命，是四条命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "还有两条命是老实和尚和小玉的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你要的是——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "我只要一个时辰。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "我带她走，你的船回转，一个时辰后我放她走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "船上的两条小艇你都已夺下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "我知道小玉一定不会让我失望。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "一个时辰，你就让她来跟我会合？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "四个人用不着两条小艇，其中一条就是为她准备的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你想得很周到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "我说话也算数。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只有不多说话的人，说话才算数。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "你看我像是个多嘴的人",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你能忘记这几天看见的事？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你能替我们保守秘密？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "你们的事我就算说出来，又有谁会相信？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "看来你好像从不轻易答应别人一件事？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "是的！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不轻易许诺的人，就不会寡信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "我总是尽力去做。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么我相信她回来的时候一定平安无恙。",
      "tone": "信任",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "一定。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我也相信现在小艇一定已放了下去。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "很可能。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么只要等你一下去，就可以看见这条船已回头了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "跟你谈交易，的确是件很愉快的事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我也一样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只希望这是最后一次了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "最后一次相见？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "下次你再见到我时，我相信彼此都不会有这么愉快了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_gong_jiu",
      "text": "我也相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你真的见到了宫九？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他究竟是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你们已见过面，但你却还是不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "我只知道一点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "我绝不想再看见他，也绝不想跟他交手了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只可惜有些事就算你真的不想去做，有时却又偏偏非去做不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "难道我一定还会看见他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在时候一定已经到了，我们已经应该放她走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你还不走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "我为什么要走？这箱子里又暖又舒服。",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你不想去见你的九哥？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "和尚有多久没有看过脱光的女人了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "好像……好像已经有几百年了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "佛家讲究眼中有色，心中无色，和尚为什么不敢看我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "和尚的道行还不够。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "难道和尚心里有鬼么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "有一点。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "坐在和尚怀里去，原来比躺在箱子里还舒服得多。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "和尚有多久没摸过女人了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "不……不知道。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "是不知道，还是忘记了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "是……是忘记了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "和尚一定连摸女人是什么滋味都忘了，让我来提醒你。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "割掉系船的绳子，她上去也好，不上去也好，都不关我们的事了。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果她一定要淹死，我们怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我们也只有看着。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好办法，好主意。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "陆小凤，你这个王八蛋！我绝不会饶了你的，总有一天我要把你切碎了煮来吃！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    }
  ],
